caption.p: Structures of swertisin ( 111), 2″- O-rhamnosyl swertisin ( 112), viniferin ( 113), resveratrol 3,4′- O-di-β- d-glucopyranoside ( 114), isotectorigenin ( 115) isolated from Iris postii Mouterde; H→C HMBC correlations determined in the 2D-NMR spectrum of 2″- O-rhamnosyl swertisin ( 112A).
